- "Hello,

I'm beginning to use your my Time Organizer. Nice application, thank you!

I have three improvement suggestions:

1. After dragging a Task/Event/.. to the day column, it should be already opened in edit mode so that i can start tipping immediately. As now implemented i first have to position the cursor over the pencil and click it, before i can start tipping.

2. Tasks marked as "Done" should be recognizable as "Done" without hovering the cursor about the task. At the moment a task who is done and is not placed in the current-date-column can not be recognized as "Done". I would display them with a strikethrough effect for example.

3. I find no overview of tasks of the past which are not completed ("Done"). It would be very helpful for me to see if there are any forgotten tasks. So now if they are not in the current week, i simply will forget over them."
